gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Wizards 109, Kings 102
gameRecap.excerpt: Washington defeats Sacramento, 109-102. Kyle Kuzma led Washington with 31 points, six rebounds, and five while Deni Avdija added 17 points, nine rebounds, and five assists. De’Aaron Fox led the Kings with 25 points, five rebounds, five assists, and six steals as Malik Monk (20 points, four assists) and Domantas Sabonis (14 points, 14 rebounds, six assists) totaled 34 points. The Wizards move to 12-58 while the Kings fall to 40-29.
